Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.50,0:00:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.24,0:00:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧去死吧去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.99,0:00:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.41,0:00:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.68,0:00:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.53,0:00:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.43,0:00:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些鬼东西...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:51.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸多年以来一直就是背负着这样的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候 我一直向往成为正义的使者
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:04.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧 我会努力实现爸爸的愿望的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.86,0:01:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.59,0:01:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.40,0:01:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果卫宫士郎真的是卫宫切嗣正义的使者的儿子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.29,0:01:22.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎 既然决定要做了那么就算死也要赢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.77,0:01:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.88,0:01:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言峰是你要打倒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.38,0:01:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能输给那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.74,0:01:35.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上性命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.93,0:01:39.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样说不定你会超越我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.15,0:02:26.55,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(334,360)\fad(800,800)}{\bord0\fs55\fnSimHei}远离一切的理想乡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.58,0:02:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 难道你将那些东西都摆脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.96,0:02:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人吃惊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你虽然逃过那一劫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过以你这么冲动的性格
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.71,0:02:54.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种武断的思想 已经束手无策了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啰嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.79,0:02:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一开始就没有想过什么策略
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:10.56,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\a6}天地乖离 开辟之星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enuma Elish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:16.97,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\a6}誓约胜利之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Excalibur
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.58,0:04:05.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果 这就是我的使命的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该还有我可以做到的事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:43.89,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\a6}天地乖离 开辟之星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.46,0:04:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enuma Elish
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.04,0:04:50.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同调 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你就是我的剑鞘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.57,0:05:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她梦中的...理想乡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的名字就叫做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:29.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Avalon
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.32,0:05:30.14,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\a6}遗世孤立的理想乡:传说中亚瑟王死后前往的理想国度
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,投...投影魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.66,0:06:58.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 想用这种把戏把我...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ex
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.12,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\a6}誓约
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Enuma
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:02.84,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\a6}天地乖离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:05.14,Default1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\a6}胜利之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,calibur
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言峰绮礼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.07,0:07:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,labt
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Avalon
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.05,0:07:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传说中王者们死后到达的理想国度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.62,0:07:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连五道的魔法都不能突破
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都不能侵害的终极守护
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个才是你真正的宝具吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:08:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是传说中圣剑的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.57,0:08:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一个可恨的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.97,0:08:20.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到最后还要反抗我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.55,0:08:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.87,0:08:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法得到的东西才是最漂亮的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.00,0:08:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了 骑士王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.95,0:08:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是痛快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.10,0:08:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.53,0:08:48.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你会有这一把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.81,0:08:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.06,0:08:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是远阪给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.43,0:08:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.65,0:09:02.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前一时兴起给了某个小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.49,0:09:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那的确是十年前吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.36,0:09:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得我变得衰弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.33,0:09:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同调 开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.29,0:10:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来破坏圣杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.88,0:10:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Master 下命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有你的命令的话我是无法破坏它的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你使用最后的令咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.84,0:10:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.85,0:10:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想听你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.68,0:10:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.06,0:10:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱着Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.21,0:11:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望她比任何人都过得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.17,0:11:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且祈愿能够和她一起生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.22,0:11:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我真的是爱她的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不应该是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱着即使受了伤还继续战斗到最后的Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:38.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有她的荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.12,0:11:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我决不能玷污——
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成那个使命吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话一切都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 一切都结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作你的剑去讨伐敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:22.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守卫你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.93,0:13:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够实现这个约定我感到很荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 你完成地很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.97,0:13:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后还有一件事要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样还真像你的作风呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.79,0:14:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 樱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.38,0:14:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早饭已经准备好了 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.12,0:14:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天不是要参加弓道部的比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早饭就让我做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.38,0:14:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不像往常一样迎接早晨的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很不习惯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.48,0:14:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:15:00.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大助 快停
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.56,0:15:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnDFKaiShuW7-B5}刹车 刹车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 失控了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.01,0:15:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 让开 让开...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.41,0:15:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 士郎强壮了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:18.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能够空手接住摩托车
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.85,0:15:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎 不用客气尽管说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我随时可以在Tiger睡觉的时候把她的头砍掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.03,0:15:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.31,0:15:27.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说呀 好心让你寄宿在我家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.75,0:15:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心我在垃圾回收的时候把你扔掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不会放手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.27,0:15:32.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后会由我...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个小恶魔 小恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.41,0:15:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.83,0:15:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一早就是油炸豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大河还真是没有礼貌呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:44.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的会把你扔掉的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.66,0:15:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为她跟我说过这个很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:16:01.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢啊 我好喜欢自己啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.57,0:16:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚看电视看太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.65,0:16:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说言峰教堂那里来了一个新的神父呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.85,0:16:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.28,0:16:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柳洞寺也正在复修
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上都恢复原状了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你会更消沉一些呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.51,0:16:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要是我消沉的话你会安慰我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.43,0:16:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揣你一脚 让你在一天之内就重新振作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.05,0:16:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.29,0:16:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我应该没有什么留恋的了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎你内心已经做了了结了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.82,0:16:59.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.67,0:17:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天记忆会变得模糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后可能逐渐忘却了她的声音她的一举一动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就算这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.07,0:17:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惟有喜欢过Saber这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远记住的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.34,0:17:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚瑟王
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这就去叫士兵过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先躺在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.49,0:17:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝狄威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.35,0:17:51.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你恢复意识了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:55.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了一个梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然平时都不太做梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.15,0:18:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经历了一次宝贵的旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:08.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么请你尽情地放松休息
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再次闭上眼睛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.18,0:18:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定又能看到梦的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦的延续
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到同样的梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我也经历过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要强烈地去希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.34,0:18:31.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是渊博
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.69,0:18:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝狄威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.88,0:18:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿着我的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.05,0:18:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.53,0:18:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过这个森林
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:54.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过那个血淋淋的山丘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:19:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的剑投到前面那个深深的湖里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.09,0:19:13.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧 贝狄威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明感觉距离这么近
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.27,0:20:05.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是伸手却又抓不到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:07.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就算这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.63,0:20:08.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算望尘莫及
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.18,0:20:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是有东西留在心中的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:13.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾身处同一空间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.19,0:20:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾仰望同一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要记住这些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算相隔多么遥远
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.74,0:20:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我仍然相信我们是在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.60,0:20:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要现在不停的奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准远方的目标
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.59,0:20:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会将那企盼的东西拿到手的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.78,0:20:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王 我已确实将剑送到湖中仙女的手中了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.31,0:20:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.16,0:20:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺起胸膛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.32,0:20:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你捍卫了王的命令

Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.54,0:21:02.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贝狄威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.30,0:21:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一次沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.34,0:21:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会...稍长一点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您看到了吗 亚瑟王
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.43,0:21:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦的延续

